    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and would make a great project or affordable daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, sun fading on the roof, and a few small dings. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and minor tears, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain operational. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to ensure long-term reliability. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
      "price": 19000.0,
